document_data.name: Sunset Gate
document_data.mainbody: The '''Sunset Gate''' was a gate separating the [[West Cwm]] and the [[Vine Vale]] on the outskirts of [[Evereska]]. There was a stone guardhouse nearby that used to serve as a watch post for a dozen Evereskan soliders.
